Write a program in C to sort an array using Pointer. The sample output must be as below
Algorithm
-> initialize pointer to an array 
-> read size 
-> allocate memory 
-> read elements to an array
-> point i to 0 index element j to 1 index element
-> compare two elements like 
-> if condition true swap elements
-> increament j 
-> compare again i with j until j reaches to size
-> increatment i until i reaches size
